{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"22e56779e6","title":"转发中南军区打虎部署的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"cce1f5e8eb","index":0,"year":1952,"month":2,"day":22,"articleId":"22e56779e6"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji31","name":"毛泽东全集第31卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/31-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji31":{"comments":[{"id":"ca232b0769","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"22e56779e6","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指谭政1952年2月20日关于中南军区打虎部署给毛泽东的报告。报告说，中南军区拟将打虎延至3月15日。争取在3月5日至10日前，地方军完成分区一级、野战军完成师团两级打虎计划。华南、各省军区、各军一级，则争取在3月15日前完成，如不可能则函量延长。3月5日或10日后，地方军转入整县大队及独立团，依次转入连队。野战军则在完成军师团三级机关打虎任务后，转入营连两级。"}],"contents":[{"id":"f2d3eeb79a","type":"title","text":"转发中南军区打虎部署的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"22e56779e6"},{"id":"ca232b0769","type":"paragraph","text":"谭政同志，并告各大军区：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"22e56779e6"},{"id":"61564e2a18","type":"paragraph","text":"二月二十日报告收到。（一）同意你们的部署。（二）请各大军区亦按中南所提部署去做，力争三月底完成全军三反任务，包括营连和县大队独立团的三反在内。四月一号起实行整编","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"22e56779e6"},{"id":"f274e15d61","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"22e56779e6"},{"id":"733c636f0a","type":"paragraph","text":"二月二十二日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"22e56779e6"},{"id":"5c5a262147","type":"paragraph","text":"[]谭政，当时任中国人民解放军中南军区第三政治委员。","index":5,"publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"22e56779e6"}],"page":{"id":"6c208e0bce","publicationId":"maoquanji31","articleId":"22e56779e6","start":428,"end":428}}}},"__N_SSG":true}